    "5048611": {
      "title": "Limit of spin squeezing in finite-temperature Bose-Einstein condensates",
      "abstract": "We show that, at finite temperature, the maximum spin squeezing achievable using interactions in Bose-Einstein condensates has a finite limit when the atom number $N\\ensuremath{\\rightarrow}\\ensuremath{\\infty}$ at fixed density and interaction strength. We calculate the limit of the squeezing parameter for a spatially homogeneous system and show that it is bounded from above by the initial noncondensed fraction."
